<section data-name="faq" class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Why go digital instead of traditional prints?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Digital is the smart choice! No more lost or damaged prints, no waste, and everyone gets their photos instantly. Plus, you'll save money since there's no expensive paper or chemicals needed. Your guests can easily share their memories on social media right away!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">How do guests get their photos?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">It's super simple! Guests receive their photos instantly via text message, and they'll also have access to a beautiful online gallery. No more waiting around for prints or losing physical copies - everything is safely stored digitally for easy sharing and downloading.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">What makes your digital booth special?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Our digital booth combines premium quality with modern convenience. You get unlimited photos, instant sharing, and professional-grade equipment that captures perfect shots every time. Plus, our streamlined setup means more space for your event and no bulky equipment!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">What about the guest experience?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Guests love our digital booth! No more waiting in long lines - our system is quick and intuitive. Take as many photos as you want, preview them instantly, and share them right away. It's a modern, fun experience that keeps your party moving!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Do you provide props?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">We skip the overpriced, reused props that most companies charge extra for. Instead, we encourage natural, genuine moments - your real smiles and personalities make the best photos! If you'd like props, we're happy to recommend some affordable options you can keep afterward.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Do you offer 360° video booths?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">We currently specialize in high-quality digital photo experiences. While 360° booths are trendy, we've chosen to perfect what we do best - delivering amazing photos that capture genuine moments at an affordable price. This focused approach helps us keep our prices reasonable while maintaining exceptional quality.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
